15
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:11,020
Pinahahalagahan namin ang atensyon
at pagmamalasakit ng lahat ng sektor.

16
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,899
Bagama't Minghui

17
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:15,620
